			<item>
				<title>About Ryu</title>
				<link>http://localhost:1313/fighting-game-notes/docs/street-fighter-6/ryu/about/</link>
				<pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
				<guid>http://localhost:1313/fighting-game-notes/docs/street-fighter-6/ryu/about/</guid>
				<description>&lt;p&gt;The original gangsta. A very straightforward character who can play the drive system pretty well, his simplicity and general safety after buttons coupled with high damage make him a very formidable character.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;In Street Fighter 6, his new addition is &amp;ldquo;Denjin&amp;rdquo; which allows him to channel his ki as an install, enhancing his fireball, super 1, and Hashogeki.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;what-is-he-good-at&#34;&gt;What is he good at? &lt;a href=&#34;#what-is-he-good-at&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34;&gt;&lt;i class=&#34;material-icons align-middle&#34;&gt;link&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;Ryu is just very good in general.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
			</item>
			<item>
